These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, pear
There are 2 different favourite colors: light-blue, aquamarine
1. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is not the person eating pear##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | pear   | nectarine  |
| Sport   | light-blue | aquamarine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: british, nigerian
2 different pets are kept: goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the goat is not the nigerian##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | british | nigerian      |
| Pet    | goat  | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, november
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, sailing
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is not the person who's birthday is in july##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | november  | july    |
| Sport   | handball | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-4::.
