.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, card-games
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, lacrosse
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is not the person who's sport is lacrosse##6
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | collecting  | card-games |
| Sport         | lacrosse | golf      |

